                  <summary>A work containg the dealings which the author had with Abu ʿAbbās al-Yaḥmadī, the vizier of Morocco</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Islamic_Arabic_253-item1">
                     <author key="person_f4942">
                        <persName xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied">ʿAlī ibn Aḥmad ibn Qāsim ibn Mūsā Miṣbāḥ al-Darwīlī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">al-Zarwīlī</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7529">Sanā al-muhtadī ilá mafākhir al-wazīr Abī al-ʿAbbās al-Yaḥmadī</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_7529">سنا المهتدي الى مفاخر الوزير ابي العباس اليحمدي</title>
                     <note>The book containa the qasīdah and the letters of the author. It is divided inta a muqaddamah, 5 abwāb and a khātimah, of which a good indes is found on <locus from="5a" to="6a">ff. 5r-6r</locus>
                     </note>
                     <note>On <locus from="313b" to="313b">fol. 313v</locus> the author states that he wrote in <date calendar="#Hijri-qamari" when="1713">Hijri-qamari</date>
